data.title: Winona State University
data.meta_description: At the Commencement Ceremony, we congratulate our students who have worked so hard to achieve the goal of graduation and celebrate their accomplishments.
data.text:
The McCown Gymnasium in Memorial Hall is located off Main Street, adjacent to East 9th Street.

The McCown Gym has bleacher seating for guests. Graduates will sit in chairs arranged on the gym floor.

Guest seating is available on a first-come first-served basis

Doors will open for guests 30 minutes prior to each ceremony.

Strollers are not allowed in the McCown Gym.

IWC 143 is reserved for stroller parking. However, this room is not monitored.

The Main Stage Theatre on the second floor in the Performing Arts Center is located west of Johnson Street.

The Main Stage Theatre has theater-style seating with wooden chairs.

Seating in the overflow is first-come first-served.

Doors will open for guests 30 minutes prior to each ceremony.

Strollers are not allowed in the Main Stage Theatre.

IWC 143 is reserved for stroller parking. However, this room is not monitored.
